pweekly.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/13707521_10157245395215014_6863447300406282566_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbka.mpweekly.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2F13707521_10157245395215014_6863447300406282566_n.jpg&h=c01761c7&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好撚正"},{"pid":"264bad8fd609fe389209d4059afbae4c51899a83","tid":480930,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T06:06:18.000Z","msg":"睇標題諗緊佢幾時結左婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdf834e88e7705ada246257c723c05945228a3fa","tid":480930,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"公家欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n畀坤哥玩厭左?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444bf9078a7980421f36deded1c91c4a19fdecc2","tid":480930,"uid":74824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:04:11.000Z","msg":"沈大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bddb304ed3e4dcc39c57420c1d47e04c0ebea2b","tid":480930,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T11:09:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>譚凱琪好靚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n識貨好有星味, 仲要日本果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 唔似拍電視d姐仔<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.esquirehk.com/var/esquirehk/storage/images/people/women-we-love/woman-we-love-zoie-tam-2017/1663168-4-chi-HK/_1_img_1032_688.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.esquirehk.com%2Fvar%2Fesquirehk%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpeople%2Fwomen-we-love%2Fwoman-we-love-zoie-tam-2017%2F1663168-4-chi-HK%2F_1_img_1032_688.jpg&h=19b69